Matched audience file columns mapped with system fields<br><br>This supports a few columns mapping as follows: <br><br>1.FirstName,LastName,State,Zip - <br>SampleValue: ```{
    "FirstName": "Voters_FirstName",
    "LastName": "Voters_LastName",
    "mState": "Residence_Addresses_State", 
    "mZip5": "Residence_Addresses_Zip"
}```<br><br>2.LastName,StreetAddress,State,Zip - SampleValue: ```{
    "LastName": "Voters_LastName",
    "StreetAddress": "Residence_Addresses_AddressLine",
    "mState": "Residence_Addresses_State", 
    "mZip5": "Residence_Addresses_Zip"
}```<br>3.StreetAddress,State,Zip - SampleValue: ```{
    "StreetAddress": "Residence_Addresses_AddressLine",
    "mState": "Residence_Addresses_State", 
    "mZip5": "Residence_Addresses_Zip"
}```<br><br>4.NPI_ID - SampleValue: ```{
    "NPI_ID_VALUE": "NPI_ID"
}```<br><br>5.VoterId - SampleValue: ```{
    "LALVOTERID": "Voters_ID"
}```<br><br>6.Phone - SampleValue: ```{
    "Phone": "Phone"
}```<br><br>7.Email - SampleValue: ```{
    "Email": "Email"
}```<br><br>8.FullAddress - SampleValue: ```{
    "FullAddress": "Residence_FullAddress"
}```<br>

Matched audience columns setting as per the selected columns for matching<br<br>>Column setting should be as per the the selected column as follows: <br><br>1.FirstName,LastName,State,Zip - NOT REQUIRED.<br><br>2.LastName,StreetAddress,State,Zip - NOT REQUIRED.<br><br>3.StreetAddress,State,Zip - NOT REQUIRED.<br><br>2.LastName,StreetAddress,State,Zip -NOT REQUIRED.<br> <br>4.VoterId (It must be supported voter's data partners id - [API DOCs](?path=/Audience%20API/getMatchedAudienceDataPartner) -) - SampleValue: ```{
    "Voters_ID": "voterbase_id"
}```<br><br>5.NPI_Id (It must be supported healthcare data partners id - [API DOCs]() -) - SampleValue: ```{
    "NPI_ID": "healthcare_id"
}```<br><br>6.Phone (It must be supported data format's id - [API DOCs](?path=/Audience%20API/getMatchedAudienceDataFormats) -) - SampleValue: ```{
    "Phone": "SHA1"
}```<br><br>7.Email (It must be supported data format's id - [API DOCs](?path=/Audience%20API/getMatchedAudienceDataFormats) -) - SampleValue: ```{
    "Email": "SHA256"
}```<br><br>8.FullAddress - NOT REQUIRED.

